  "description": [
    "THE PRODUCERS NEWS Published weekly at Plentywood Montana by The Peoples Publishing Company Inc Official Organ of the UNITED FARMERS LEAGUE Official paper of the City of Plentywood Mont Subscription Rates Natteaal EditionIn the United States per year 200 six months 100 three months 60 cents Foreign per year 260 six months 125 three months 60 cents County EditionIn the United States year 800 six months 150 four months 180 County Edition to foreign countries year 350 six months 175 four months 125 Rates furnished upon application Advertising ERIK BERT Editor HANS RASMUSSEN Business Manager Friday April 29 1932 YOUR PAPER MUST CARRY NEWSOFYOUR LIVES In another part of this weeks paper is printed a letter from the wife of a Shendan county farmer She tells a story of suffer ing that is true not only of her farm in Sheridan county but applies to great parts of eastern Montana North Dakota and other large sections of the farm area This letter is the first response to the recent re quest of the Producrs News for first hand accounts of farmers conditions But what is happening in other coun Have there been any foreclosures in ties _ your neighborhood How"
